            <div type="edition" xml:lang="la" xml:space="preserve"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <persName type="divine" ref="#manes"><w lemma="deus"><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan></w> <w lemma="manes"><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan></w></persName> <w lemma="sacer"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrum</ex></expan></w> 
                <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested"><name nymRef="Claudius">Claudius</name> <name nymRef="Maxime">M
                <lb break="no" n="3"/>axime</name></persName> <w lemma="miles">mil<supplied reason="omitted">e</supplied>s</w> 
                <lb n="4"/><orgName type="military" ref="#legio3august"><w lemma="legio"><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan></w> <num value="3">III</num> <addName nymRef="Augustus"><expan><abbr>A<supplied reason="omitted">u</supplied>gu</abbr><ex>stae</ex></expan></addName></orgName> 
                <lb n="5"/><w lemma="stipendium"><expan><abbr>stupe</abbr><ex>ndiorum</ex></expan></w> <note>sic</note> <w lemma="uiginti"><expan><abbr>uig</abbr><ex>inti</ex></expan></w> <w lemma="duo">dua</w> <w lemma="uiuo"><expan><abbr>u</abbr><ex>ixit</ex></expan></w> 
                <lb n="6"/><date type="life-span" dur="P40Y"><w lemma="annus">ano<supplied reason="omitted">s</supplied></w> <num value="40">XXXX</num></date> <w lemma="pater"><expan><abbr>pate</abbr><ex>r</ex></expan></w> <persName type="attested"><name nymRef="Ana">Ana</name></persName> <w lemma="facio"><expan><abbr><unclear>f</unclear></abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan></w>
            </ab></div>
            
            <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
                <p>Sacred to the gods below: Claudius Maximus soldier of the Third Legion Augusta, having served twenty two years lived 40 years. His father, ?Ana made <supplied reason="subaudible">the tomb</supplied>.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>De toute façon, le texte doit etre daté, non de la fin du III s., comme le croit l'auteur mais du debut [note de J. Marcillet-Jaubert].</p>
                <p>Line 4: AE suggests pater na<unclear>t</unclear>(uralis)</p>
            </div>
